## ğŸ“Œ Project Objective
The purpose of this project is to visualize key insights from the Zomato restaurant dataset. It focuses on cuisine popularity, cost vs rating, city-wise trends, and online ordering patterns. The aim is to communicate data clearly and interactively.

---

## ğŸ“Š Visualizations

| Chart Type     | Purpose                                |
|----------------|----------------------------------------|
| Bar Chart      | Top 10 cuisines                        |
| Pie Chart      | Online ordering availability           |
| Scatter Plot   | Relationship between cost and rating   |
| City Bar Chart | Restaurant count by city               |

All visualizations are available in the `/images` folder. Interactive versions can be viewed in the Jupyter notebook.

